### GET all users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8

### GET user by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/id/2
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8

### GET user by email
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/email/testmail1@mail.com
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8